It is to our credit that we have finally appointed a mediator to represent u. and I am pleased to hear that he is my friend , compatriot and colleague , Ambassador Moratino. and that we are able to give our support to Mr Colajanni 's report . This is a document which we will certainly be able to improve somewhat by means of the amendments which have been tabled . 
